0.body: #Chapter 1 Debugging techniques In a perfect world every line of code you type in immediately works as expected. If you are like most people, however, you will make tons of mistakes. SuperCollider does not have a built-in debugger. So how do we go about debugging problems? We'll go over some ways to debug your SuperCollider programs.
